Yes, this. Ok, here is my gestalt grunting:\
This is the reason for the texts--the books. The book is the test. The test is the examination--the performance. If we cannot recognize the cycle and _invent_ a way around it--to _overcome We-I_--then the cycle will by objective trend observations, put Humanity in a position where the thermostat unrecognized and uncontrolled, will literally catch our house on fire.\
So, if I am to take the ancients and their texts as _not primitive_--rather, deeply sophisticated--then they would serve as wisdom of the ancients that says, 'we see the pattern, but we also see that we as a species are amnesiacs across generations; this is our attempt to break the cycle by our teaching of the past', and _this_, proactive _regardless of one's specific belief in a higher power_.\
The exit condition, I think simple, from my personal perspective: The Human Unification Event, where Human Unification is by-definitional--whatever it takes for Humanity to unify in a manner that does not corrupt or re-fracture.\
